headline: Nasdaq 100: Who's In And Who's Out Of QQQ. Walmart, Strategy, Lululemon?
summary: The Nasdaq 100 index's annual reconstitution is a couple of weeks away, but market valuations at the end of this week will determine changes. So the outcome is almost set. Walmart surprised Wall Street last week with the news it will move its WMT listing to the Nasdaq.
